    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Computer output devices consisting of flat drawing tables traversed by writing-tool assemblies which produce drawings on paper or film to high-standard accuracy.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
